{"tid":260834,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"信用卡一問","createTime":"2017-05-28T03:21:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-28T10:10:13.000Z","uid":90663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"019c25f588bbcb4e51d5c66b6e798146c9a8ce1f","tid":260834,"uid":90663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T03:21:46.000Z","msg":"尋日係某個台灣網想充值D點數<br />\n平時用開信用卡佢都會send個驗證碼去手機到<br />\n但尋日用果陣我打哂D信用卡資料<br />\n禁左確認之後佢已經話交易完成左<br />\n隔左陣恒生先send個message黎話比左錢咁<br />\n<br />\n其實咁樣比錢法會唔會仲更加容易比人盜用?<br />\n好擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33fcceb64989aee7b568b76c9a2c89c2a4b9dd66","tid":260834,"uid":117316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T03:29:38.000Z","msg":"無得用paypal咩？"},{"pid":"bd59b09fc8b08e441cda7cd8fdbd3c8f9b0604ca","tid":260834,"uid":90663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T03:41:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無得用paypal咩？</blockquote><br />\n好似有，但我無登記paypal，而且用開就咁比信用卡"},{"pid":"eeba850c13a15be20b072e1dc420dd809e3c24e8","tid":260834,"uid":117316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T10:10:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>無得用paypal咩？</blockquote><br />\n好似有，但我無登記paypal，而且用開就咁比信用卡</blockquote><br />\n咁咪而家去登記囉<br />\n可以照綁你張信用卡然後當信用卡咁用<br />\n安全性高好多"}]}